snippet.title: Amber Alert Sent Out For Missing Teen Girl
snippet.description:
From: https://www.youtube.com/user/ABCNews

October 20, 2018 - Police are following up on all leads and tips to get information about what happened the night Jayme Closs' parents were killed and she was kidnapped.
